Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:37.53,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She was shining so brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.79,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I think some of her power rubbed off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going to work even harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.29,yoshida clinic,,0,0,0,,{\an2}Yoshida Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.98,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.29,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.95,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Usa-P?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.51,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,W-Welcome home, pyon, Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.87,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See you later, Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:00.53,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.28,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:06.02,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.06,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.73,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,K-Komugi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:15.37,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Did you miss me while I was visiting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:16.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,the Fanta-C World, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It was nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.39,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Actually, I forgot you were even gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.44,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You're so mean, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.28,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,This whole time, I've been thinking about taking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.47,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,a bath with you when I got back, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.96,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.59,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,These are for you, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.05,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Fanta-C World manju, Fanta-C World cookies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.55,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Fanta-C World soda, and Fanta-C World crêpes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.76,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.35,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.31,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Whisper whisper, mumble mumble, pyon pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.65,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? A girl monster stole all your Fanta-C Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.22,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Yeah, pyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.44,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,We'll steal them back, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:01.18,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,My ears will stand at attention \Nwhen another monster appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.91,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I'll get them then for sure, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:07.05,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what's going on, but fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.29,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I'm going to rest for a bit, then, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.45,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you do while I was gone, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I made a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.67,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's a super popular idol named Lilia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:17.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.05,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She's cute, pyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Poko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Nyanyan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.47,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.81,Main,USAPP,0,0,0,,She's the mysterious girl monster \Nwho stole my Fanta-C Cards, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.98,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's definitely her, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.85,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You still haven't found Maid-chan or Sister-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,in their un-transformed forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.51,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's most definitely her, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.86,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's her, pyon! Let's go find out, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,How do we do that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.82,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She's a monster, pyon! \NAn enemy we must defeat, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.87,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.87,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.44,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. There's no way \NLilia-chan is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.00,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,...no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.93,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:12.85,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.19,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,You look cute again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Did you sense anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.35,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.15,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,My ears aren't stiff, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:27.11,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,But I sense something sort of off, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's just a little... I guess \Nyou could say I'm half stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.06,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Half stiff? So you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.50,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,She isn't a monster, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.25,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.41,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,But I knyow I'm sensing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.01,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,I hope you have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks for inviting us to \Nyour Tokyo Skydome concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.70,Main,AI,0,0,0,,How {\i1}very{\i0} gracious of Lilia to invite us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.61,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,Now, now... As long as we're here, \Nlet's enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan's going to be singing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.87,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,But we can see what our Tokyo \NSkydome concert might be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.52,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,She filled an arena that \Naccommodates 570,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.78,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.38,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,That's about the same as \Nthe population of Tottori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's still just a distant dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.93,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But Kokona-chan, Tsukasa-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.47,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,someday we'll sing here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.68,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.06,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.10,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,I'll do my best again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.75,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,I'll put on the greatest performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.95,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,So my fans will enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.74,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,So my friends will enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.13,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,And so I can gain even more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.97,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,fans and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.16,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.50,Main,STAFF,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.69,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:10.43,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,As I scatter diamonds to make \Neven ordinary days glitter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:15.64,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,I imagine a special version of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:25.22,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,This is a place where dreams, hopes,\Nand aspirations can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.70,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.19,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What, Usa-P?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.07,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,My ears are stiff, pyon! It's a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:30.17,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,But it's not a place easily reached
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.33,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,That's an Infrared Camera Monster, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.90,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,This stage isn't easily reached
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.83,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,That monster will make your \Nclothes transparent, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.70,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,Far beyond the brilliance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.13,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Uh, I need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:48.84,Main - Top - Italics,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a chance within their grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.97,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,M-Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I need to powder my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll go to another bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.85,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.85,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I feel like going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.22,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,O-Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.53,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shuffle, shuffle, shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.27,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shuffle, shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.49,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Fidget, fidget. Fidget, fidget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.21,Main - Top,USAP,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny chloroform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.21,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Marisol miral sparklism!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.21,Main - Top,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Pretty flower sunshine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.76,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Chanting it deciphers the code \Nprogrammed into the incantation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.76,Main - Top,USAP,0,0,0,,Shiny lovely tenipole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.76,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Flaming miral penifore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.76,Main - Top,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Fluffy coquettish player!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.31,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,scanning their entire bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.73,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The rays turn Komugi's caring \Nheart, Kokona's dutiful heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.57,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and Tsukasa's loving spirit into Amazoni-N Cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.20,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,activating their maximum Tombo-E potential
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:27.18,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and reconstructing their bodies and costumes, \Ncompleting the Chan-G.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.71,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,On average, the transformation\Ntakes 0.02 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.69,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.93,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Transparent, transparent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.71,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Infrared rays make things transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.48,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Even if you're wearing clothes, \NI can see right through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.98,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Transparent, transparent...
