Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.27,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,We won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.73,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,...touch Lilia-chan!
