Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:38.87,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,...rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:42.89,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Worldwide Revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.87,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Super Excellent Marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.60,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Top of Top Idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.88,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,There's another monster over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.17,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Sticking a Fan-C Card on her stuffed animal,
