Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:09.10,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,By the way, it takes 0.015 \Nseconds for her to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.49,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,That's 0.005 seconds faster \Nthan the magical girls.
