Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.51,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:07.13,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,This power will turn everyone \Nin the world into Lilia's fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.02,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Then she'll never be lonely again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.48,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,I will make everyone in the world a fan of Lilia,
