Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.74,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,into a ray of light that shines upon all hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.16,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:42.15,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Let's pray to the shining stars
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:47.98,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Forever and ever starlight stars
