Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.60,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:37.38,Main,LILIA,0,0,0,,My fans are my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.87,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Usa-P and the other two took the Fan-C Cards
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.89,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and returned to the Fanta-C World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:47.14,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I hear they're living happily under Hime-P.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.61,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Hime-P, you're such a benevolent widow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.90,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,to turn Kumami into a mascot, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.15,Main,PRINCESS,0,0,0,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.87,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,You're a widow among widows, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.41,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,It gives me chills, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:02.03,Main,PRINCESS,0,0,0,,Praise me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.39,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,You're the greatest widow, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:06.12,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Say, let's get our meow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.19,Main,PRINCESS,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Calm down, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.83,Main,PRINCESS,0,0,0,,Wait. Your. Turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.77,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hey, come to think of it, I wonder who
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.23,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,gathered the most Fan-C Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.93,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Well, not that it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.72,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan's busy, so we don't see her often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.72,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But let's hang out again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:28.91,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.70,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan has been training \Nfor marathons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:36.32,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's even going to join the regular \Ncast of a marathon program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.99,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Good! Keep your back straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.24,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,That's it! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:42.49,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! I'll train even harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.97,academy,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,800)}Nijigaoka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:46.57,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yu-nii was scouted by the \Nproducer of the swim meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:49.01,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,He's going to be debuting in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.58,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,He won't be back for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.58,Main - Top,YUTO,0,0,0,,My name is Yuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.18,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.05,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'll head there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:59.54,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Misuzu-sensei became a female pro wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:03.30,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She may be the first schoolteacher \Nto also be a pro wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.30,Main,MISUZUI,0,0,0,,Iron Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.34,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Misuzu-sensei, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.47,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.76,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.84,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,That's it! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.23,Main,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Giant Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.48,Main,MIISUZU,0,0,0,,Flying Body Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.42,Main,MISUZU,0,0,0,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.26,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,They're making a Buri Bara anime after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're going to start dubbing it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.67,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for Kokonacchi's Short Ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.00,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll make merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:40.25,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan's going to be playing \NSkirt Steak instead of Yu-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She can imitate a boy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.63,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Lilia-chan is so versatile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.34,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Come on. You'd better get \Ngoing, or you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.51,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.42,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm Yoshida Komugi. 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:26.43,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sagittarius, blood type O. \NMy favorite food is Japanese sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:29.16,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My motto is "Let's Komugication!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, it's been a while, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:34.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There's trouble, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.66,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Usa-P? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.70,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,The Fanta-C World and Earth are \Nin danger of being destroyed, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:42.22,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You need to transform immediately, \Npyon! Become a Tombo-E Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:45.67,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,No, a powered-up Tombo-E Girl R, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:48.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,R?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:49.97,end at the end,TEXT,0,0,0,,End